<paragraph blockId="13.[136,1452,518,1049]" pageId="13" pageNumber="286">
Perennial plants, with stout woody rootstock forming a small cushion with numerous rosettes of leaves, stemless or nearly so, capitula hidden between leaves, whole plant usually grayish. Leaves petiolate, coriaceous, densely covered with appressed-grayish-tomentose hairs on both sides, pinnatisect, 
<quantity box="[888,993,590,617]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.25" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="2.5" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="cm" value="4.25" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="2.5">2.5–6 cm</quantity>
long, segments in 5–10 pairs, smooth or minutely denticulate at margins, rounded or acute at apex; terminal segment larger than lateral ones, 
<quantity box="[1275,1383,626,653]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.5" metricValueMax="12.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="8.5" valueMax="12.0" valueMin="5.0">5–12 mm</quantity>
wide, nearly orbicular; lateral segments oblong to nearly orbicular, 
<quantity box="[834,929,662,689]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="5.0" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="3.0">3–7 mm</quantity>
wide, decurrent along the rachis; rarely some leaves undivided, obovate. Capitula few, 2–4-cephalous, solitary on subsessile peduncles; involucres ovoid, 17–19 × 
<quantity box="[161,287,734,761]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.1" metricValueMax="1.2" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="11.0" valueMax="12.0" valueMin="10.0">10–12 mm</quantity>
. Phyllaries multiseriate, coriaceous, imbricate, green, glabrous. Appendages rather large, concealing a major part of phyllaries, hyaline, whitish, light brown in central part, innermost entirely brown, broadly elliptic, 4–5 × 
<quantity box="[159,252,806,833]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3–4 mm</quantity>
(excluding cilia), distinctly ciliate, never with a spine; cilia whitish, numerous, 8–12 on each side, 
<quantity box="[1359,1452,806,833]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="2.5" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="2.0">2–3 mm</quantity>
long. Flowers pink; central florets hermaphroditic, 
<quantity box="[720,843,842,869]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.1" metricValueMax="2.2" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="21.0" valueMax="22.0" valueMin="20.0">20–22 mm</quantity>
long, corolla 
<quantity box="[1005,1113,842,869]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.1" metricValueMin="0.9" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="10.0" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="9.0">9–11 mm</quantity>
long, 5-lobed, lobes 
<quantity box="[1357,1452,842,869]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="4.5" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="4.0">4–5 mm</quantity>
long, stigma slightly exserted from corolla; peripheral florets 
<quantity box="[816,935,878,905]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.15" metricValueMax="2.3" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="21.5" valueMax="23.0" valueMin="20.0">20–23 mm</quantity>
long, equal than central ones, scarcely radiant, with staminodes, 4-lobed, limb lobes linear. Achenes oblong, 5–6 × 
<quantity box="[925,1044,914,941]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.75" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.5" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="2.75" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="2.5">2.5–3 mm</quantity>
, brown, rounded at apex, glabrous; detachment area lateral, 
<quantity box="[410,545,950,977]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="0.4" valueMax="0.5" valueMin="0.3">0.3–0.5 mm</quantity>
long. Pappus lacking or very short (
<quantity box="[950,1087,950,977]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="286" unit="mm" value="0.25" valueMax="0.3" valueMin="0.2">0.2–0.3 mm</quantity>
long).
</paragraph>
